{"tid":1212201,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"AOC 圖解目前環境！！！！","createTime":"2019-06-12T17:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T17:26:47.000Z","uid":52954,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5190ae829cc2d66584bc12ca1dfdbae2b3856971","tid":1212201,"uid":52954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bm8hZsX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBm8hZsX.png&h=d8c203df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事源係中間堆村民想進入右上方嘅城堡，阻止&quot;送紅色陣營條例&quot;生效，所以先計劃打低城堡守衛！但守緊嘅係長槍兵，火炮兵，槍兵。村民攻擊力太低，根本唔夠打。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xc91GGH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxc91GGH.png&h=1ea59423&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當你班村民真係精練嘅，打低晒所有守衛。SORRY，你睇下張圖最左手面！係紅色陣營中國連弩兵！仲有幾部投石車！長遠根本冇結果！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cO4kXiS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcO4kXiS.png&h=a7124bcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，正確玩法可以望望下面，有好多生產資源嘅嘢。村民只要唔種菜，唔採礦，唔伐木，停晒所有貿易商隊，停止輸送到紅色陣營。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vocOmMJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvocOmMJ.png&h=bae8ad3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後結果當然係冇肉, 冇金, 冇石, 冇木。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為除咗村民，其他兵係做唔到村民嘅工作！到時冇資源，想整多啲兵仔又唔得，幫啲兵仔升級又唔得，起多啲建築都唔得。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RoeEtsR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRoeEtsR.png&h=f1a43c61&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"beff000e45a470c211f0a639517e2225ec617318","tid":1212201,"uid":52954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:43:17.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"ac502a192fb7f36314a6ccb0a4746780acff2856","tid":1212201,"uid":13033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:45:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2731d40d88b084e217b5ed03d8cca4adea5f3211","tid":1212201,"uid":53805,"like